"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-teal pl-4","children":"Wedding videography pricing can be confusing. Here's a honest breakdown of what you can expect to pay and what factors affect the final number."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/[0.06] mb-10"}]}],["$","article",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16","children":[[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Wedding videography is one of those things couples often add to their budget last — and then wish they'd prioritized sooner. If you're trying to figure out what to budget for a wedding videographer on the Gulf Coast, here's an honest breakdown."]}],["$","h2","1",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"The Short Answer"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Wedding videography on the Gulf Coast generally ranges from around $1,500 on the low end to $5,000 or more for experienced professionals with premium packages. Where you fall in that range depends on several factors."]}],["$","h2","3",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"What Affects the Price"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Experience and reputation"}]," — A videographer who has been shooting weddings for ten years and has a strong portfolio will cost more than someone just starting out. That experience shows up in how they handle unpredictable moments, lighting challenges, and the pressure of a once-in-a-lifetime event."]}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Hours of coverage"}]," — A six-hour package covering the ceremony and reception will cost less than a full-day package that starts with getting ready and ends after the last dance."]}],["$","p","6",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Number of videographers"}]," — One camera operator captures one perspective. Two-camera coverage allows for better storytelling, more angles during the ceremony, and simultaneous coverage of the couple getting ready."]}],["$","p","7",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Delivery format"}]," — A highlight reel of three to five minutes is less work than a full-length documentary edit. Some packages include both. Understand exactly what you're getting."]}],["$","p","8",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Travel"}]," — Gulf Coast venues span from Pensacola Beach to the bayous outside New Orleans. Travel time and logistics affect pricing, especially for destination weddings."]}],["$","p","9",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Turnaround time"}]," — Standard delivery is often four to twelve weeks. Rush delivery costs extra."]}],["$","h2","10",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"What to Watch Out For"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Very low prices often mean very little experience, minimal equipment, or an unclear contract. Before you book based on price alone, ask to see full wedding films — not just highlight reels — and read reviews from past clients."]}],["$","p","12",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Also make sure your contract clearly states what happens if the videographer gets sick, how many revisions are included, and exactly what you'll receive at delivery."]}],["$","h2","13",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"A Practical Approach"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Set a realistic budget before you start shopping. Communicate that budget clearly when you reach out to videographers. A good professional will tell you honestly whether they can work within your range or not. You'll save time on both sides."]}],["$","p","15",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Wedding videography is the one thing from your wedding day that lets you relive the moments you missed while you were in them. It's worth getting right."]}]],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal/10 to-transparent border border-teal/20 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest mb-3","children":"Find a Professional on the Gulf Coast"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted text-sm mb-6","children":"Browse verified media professionals available for your next project — from Tallahassee to New Orleans."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/browse","className":"btn-teal font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Browse Pros"}],["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/post-job","className":"btn-outline font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Post a Job"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-navy2 border-t border-white/[0.06] py-12 px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-6xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest mb-8 text-center","children":"More Guides"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5","children":[["$","